video_name: Out in the pen today with Rocco the wombat 🐻 Haven’t seen him much since the girls were released, every time I go out there now he’s hit that stage where he flicks the switch as a male wombat 💪 Full territorial mode, wanting to defend his space and own it That’s actually a great sign, he’s well on his way to being ready for the bush 🌿 No interest in humans anymore, does his best to fight us off, and that’s exactly what we want. Hopefully in the next couple of weeks we can get Rocco back out in the wild where he belongs, and free up some room for Betty and Kev Meanwhile, little Steve-O the wombat 🐾 riding in the hoodie pocket is coming along brilliantly. Already such a cheeky little character in the making. Legends all round! ONYA Legends! 💚✨

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: Spring has finally hit 🌱☀️ Ashlee’s out in the backyard running around with little Steve-O, and he’s even started nibbling on a bit of grass now, good signs for the little bloke 🐾💚 On the downside though, we’ve sadly lost our baby emu with the splayed legs. After a wild windstorm rolled through, we reckon the cage door blew open and he’s either wandered off or, more likely, a bird of prey’s taken him. Doesn’t happen often, but unfortunately it does happen in this game 😔 Poor Amber’s absolutely gutted, she’s walked the farm for hours and checked the cameras, but he’s just vanished into thin air. Tough part of wildlife care… Still, Steve-O’s stoked, and we’ve got to take the positives where we can. ONYA.

video_name: First red-bellied black snake catch today 🐍🔥 After the police spotted one hanging out at their handgun training facility, we headed down, scooped him up, and everything went to plan. A couple of k’s down the road I released him into a perfect little swampy area, right where he belongs. He was a little bit fiery when we let him go though — bit upsetting when I’ve taken him out to a beautiful new spot, you’d think he’d have a bit more respect 😅 It’s probably looking like it’s going to be a pretty big snake season too. In the last few days they’ve definitely started becoming more active, waking up from their long winter slumber. They’re all on the move now, looking for a tasty snack to snag 🐸🦎🐍 👉 Fun facts: • Red-bellied black snakes are one of Australia’s most iconic snakes • They are venomous ⚠️ their bite can cause pain, swelling, headaches, nausea and even muscle damage, but thanks to quick medical treatment, fatalities are very rare • They love swampy, moist habitats like creeks, lagoons, and wetlands • They actually eat frogs, small lizards, and even other snakes Beautiful, sleek snakes that play an important role in the ecosystem. Always a thrill to see one up close, and even better to give him a safe new home 🌿 ONYA!

bio: Just a little Aussie family helping critters, donate or buy some merch below
video_name: WARNING ‼️ NOT A HAPPY ENDING.. After footy training I got a call just up the road 🚗💥🐇 A young girl, only a couple of days on her license, had no fault of her own when a kangaroo came bounding out of the bush right on the apex of a hill. Sadly she collided with it and completely wrote her car off. She’s very lucky she wasn’t injured. Kangaroos are everywhere in my area and accidents like this happen often. At first the roo didn’t look too bad and I had some hope, but once I stood it up I could see its hip was completely smashed. The call had to be made to put it down 💔 That’s the reality of these jobs – not many happy endings when big kangaroos meet cars, usually both sides come off badly. The damage to the car was considerable, a real reminder of just how dangerous these situations are. Not a great story, but I share both the good and the bad, and this was one of the sad ones. But a good reminder of the risks for people especially new drivers of of Australian country roads, be safe these people did a awesome job in handling the whole situation ❤️At the end you’ll see me tell one of our little joeys to promise me they’ll stay off the road – nothing but mischief out there for them. Onya legends 💚 #ONYA #WildlifeRescue #Kangaroo #RoadSafety

video_name: Why do adoption fees exist? Every adoption fee supports the shelter. That includes paying rent, staff, food, daily care, and most of all, medical bills. But the truth is, adoption fees barely make a dent. They’re more of a symbolic donation when a dog goes home. The real lifeline comes from community donations and ongoing support. At the start of this year, three dogs at @Chicago Canine Rescue cost nearly $30,000 in medical care. That’s an impossible number for a small shelter without help from the people who care. Adoption fees help, but in reality it’s the community support that keeps the shelter running and gives these dogs a second chance. Follow @4evertails to see more behind the scenes stories and how you can help make an impact!

video_name: 📚 Как мы учились в Турции: путь Тоси от 4 до (почти) 9 Когда мы переехали в Турцию — Тосе было 4. И с этого началось большое путешествие по школам, системам, садикам и… вшам 😂 ⸻ 🔸 2021 год 4 года. Частный турецкий садик. Языка нет — и у неё, и у меня 🫠 Но дети есть дети: через пару месяцев она уже «чирикала» на турецком так, что мне самой было интересно послушать. ⸻ 🔸 2021–2022 5 лет — в Турции это уже подготовительный класс. 0 класс в частной школе. За год — 5 раз вши за год. Покинули с достоинством и без вшей😅 ⸻ 🔸 2022–2024 6 и 7 лет. Пошли в другую частную турецкую школу. Выдержали 2 класса. Сколько будет 9 + 3 — не знаем. Зато турецкий уже щебечет, как настоящая турчанка 💪 ⸻ 🔸 2024–2025 Формально — снова 2 класс. Но по русской системе она как раз по возрасту. Решаем: онлайн-обучение в Фоксфорде + летом с репетитором закрываем 1 класс. Для социализации — коворкинг. По факту: учим, понимаем, но только если «сидеть сверху» 😅 Отвлекается, ругаемся, пересматриваем уроки, которые и так короткие. Мама иногда в шоке😅 ⸻ 🔸 2025–2026 Идём в 3 класс русской школы в Анталии. Учителя, парты, доска, расписание — всё как в моём детстве. В Анталии всего 2 русские школы, выдающие дипломы, и связанные с турецкой системой. Выбрали Московскую в Ларе — по атмосфере, подходу, ощущениям. Если приживёмся — переезжаем ближе к школе. Да, опять переезд 😂

video_name: Un perro no es un objeto, es una vida 🐾 Hoy queremos compartir una realidad triste que nos duele.. Berlin solo era un bebe cuando encontró lo que creíamos sería su hogar para siempre. Sin embargo, hoy nos lo devolvieron. Un perro no es un regalo, ni un pasatiempo, ni algo que se pueda "probar" y luego descartar. Es un ser vivo que siente, que confía, que se entrega con todo su corazón. Cada adopción debe ser una decisión consciente y responsable, porque detrás de cada abandono hay un animal que sufre, que no entiende por qué lo dejaron de querer. Pedimos que quienes decidan adoptar lo hagan sabiendo que se trata de un compromiso de por vida: en las buenas y en las malas, con paciencia, con respeto y con amor. Adoptar es cambiar una vida para siempre. 🐶 #labachimanada #amor #perros #adoptanocompres

video_name: Would you PET him or PANIC? 🤔👇 Big dogs often get judged by their size and people instantly assume they are dangerous or scary 🐾 But Shadow is here to prove the opposite. He is playful, loving, and just wants to make friends and spread joy. We post these videos to show the real personality behind the size and to challenge the way people think about giant dogs. Every clip is a reminder that big dogs are not monsters, they are family, companions, and sometimes the biggest goofballs you will ever meet. Watch Shadow in action, laugh at the funny moments, see how people react, and join us in changing the perception of big dogs in the UK and USA ❤️🐕 #dog #fyp #xzycba #canecorso

video_name: We went to a different church yesterday and really did not feel well leaving. I grabbed Sara’s hand on the way back to the car and literally asked her “Why did Gos bring us here today, this was totally Megachurch vibes.” The entire service was pre recorded and felt very off. We will keep looking for a new home church but anyway we got in the car to drive home and she said. “Colby were close to riverside county animal shelter let’s stop.” I knew before we walked in one precious soul was going to be saved that day. @sara__yoder this is one of many reasons why I love you, I never thought I would meet someone with the same exact heart as mine who wants to just save every dog we can. We will absolutely have our own rescue in the future. We will save so many in our life together but for now I want you to meet “Empress Palpatina” or Tina for short 😂❤️.  #explore #dogs #happy #rescue #frenchie

video_name: I was on my way home from getting Mexican food today when I found these two beautiful dogs running in the street. I spent over an hour knocking from door to door near where they were found to try to find their home, but I had no luck. They are definitely siblings and they are definitely someone's pets. Longshot but I live in the Lake Elsinore area if you guys could help share this, we could maybe find their owners. After scoping them out and spending some time with them I'm in no rush to find their owners a I'm a huge advocate for having a slip leash or two in your car at all times for this specific reason! I have no doubt they will be returned home in the near future but I'm just happy that animal control didn't find them or they didn't end up in the local shelter. I don't have time today to go see if they're microchip, but I will do it within the next two days if an owner doesn't come forward. And if one doesn't come forward you know where they will end up. #explore #happy #rescue #rescuedog

video_name: Two nights ago on my drive to LA it got placed in my heart to save an older dog and help them live the rest of their life with so much love and affection. I fell in love with Princess when I saw her video and hurt her story. Selfishly I was pretty sad when I saw she got adopted. I was already planning out a life with her. I told myself I was gonna wake up the next day and find another older dog who needed me. I found that dog today and his name is Chief. As you all know, golden retrievers have been very crucial on this journey of dog training for me. My love for dogs developed because of a golden retriever. I got in fifth grade after begging my parents for one for over a year. I'm so happy to have my first golden retriever as an adult. Chief will be the first of many for me and my future family. I don't fight it anymore when God places these things in my heart. I may not be able to help as many dogs as I will be able to when I have my sanctuary in the future, but for now this is one more that I can help. If any of you are looking for purpose in life I recommend going to save an innocent dog today. They have healed me and I know they heal many other people. I will help you train it for free. Huge thank you to @deservingdogs for helping me make this happen. God bless all of you. Thank you all so much for your support. We're going to need to do a lot of things medically with Chief and if you would like to help, please reach out and I will tell you how you can. #explore #goldenretriever #goldenretrieverlife #rescuedog #rescueanimals #puppy #seniordog

video_name: Hasn't even been 24 hours yet and this girl is pulling on my heart strings. I'm so happy she is safe now. I'm gonna let her continue to decompress however, I'm still going to do as much with her as she allows me to. She likes to follow me around and it's the cutest thing ever. Potty training is coming along very well. I'm excited to see how close we get because I can already tell she's going to love me. She's gonna go to the vet next week and I want to get her teeth looked at as well. Outside of that, she seems super healthy. I'm so excited to see what the future has in store for us. #explore #rescuedog #rescue #frenchie #frenchbulldog

video_name: I’m so excited to have him. When I first saw him and others apart of @bubblesdogrescue I instantly wanted to get involved. There’s so many dogs like him who deserve a real chance at life. I’m going to keep you guys involved throughout this whole process with him from the beginning all the way until I place him in his forever home. If you guys would like to get involved or if you would also like to foster please reach out to me. I will also be doing this for people outside of the LA area. ❤️🐾 #explore #rescue

video_name: I've been asking God to help me continue growing as a trainer. Things like this I no longer try to deflect, pawblito showed up on my page three different times that day. I was in my car getting home from the gym and saw him for the third time. l instantly got very emotional I knew why this was happening. I wasn't expecting to get another dog right now. However I was incapable of not saving him when I knew I was somebody that could. Pawblito is one of many dogs who needs to help that I'm giving him and the second chance at life that he's gonna receive. Moving forward I'm going to make it my mission to do things like this. I haven't been utilizing my platform in the way that I want to and that's no more, together we're really going to make a change on here.

bio: Vc  ajuda muito nos seguindo na rede vizinha 👇🏻
video_name: Os pacientes que vieram pra casa nenhum está em risco, já estão de alta. Muitas vezes os donos pedem pra ela continuar a medicação pq não conseguem medicar em casa ou pra fazer troca de curativos pq tbm não conseguem, ou pq não podem buscar na clínica  no fim do dia, por falta de transporte ou horário. Alguns tutores são pessoas idosas não conseguem cuidar e medicar em casa, então ela faz esse processo pra devolver o animal a eles  já 100% recuperados. É sempre bom informar antes que venham de mimimi #humor #pets #cachorros #familia #tik_tok

Eu vi ela fazer tanto por tantos e muitas vezes por conta própria. 6 dos 12 animais que temos foram de tutores que se negaram a arcar com cuidados médicos, e ela se dispôs a adotar e cuidar, os outros 6 foram de resgate, além de vários outros que já passaram por nossas vidas e encontraram novos lares através da dedicação dela. video_name: Сальпы — это удивительные морские существа, которые могут образовывать гигантские цепочки длиной до 15 метров! Каждая отдельная сальпа остаётся самостоятельным организмом, но вместе они соединяются в длинную «ленту», синхронно сокращаясь и перекачивая воду. The Soul's Mirror 🪞 @Thermen- & Vulkanland 💚 📍 Styria’s Thermen- & Vulkanland is Austria’s premier spa destination, celebrated for its healing thermal springs, scenic vineyards, and outstanding local cuisine. It’s a place where relaxation, nature, and culinary indulgence come together. The Genusshotel Riegersburg turned out to be the perfect setting for bringing our video idea to life. 😍 AD #visitsteiermark #thermenvulkanland #videography #creativeideas

Keyhole to Paradise 🗝️ Erzberg-Leoben 📍 @erzberg_leoben AD For this video idea, we visited the stunning Leopoldsteinersee in Erzberg-Leoben 🏞️ Using a cardboard box with a keyhole-shaped cutout, we captured the beauty of the landscape in a creative way ✨ Sometimes, all it takes is a small frame to see the bigger picture 😉 #erzbergleoben #visitsteiermark #tutorial #photography

Racing 🔥🏁 at @Region Murtal 📍 The Murtal region in Styria combines stunning alpine landscapes with its reputation as a motorsport hub. At the Red Bull Ring in Spielberg, fans can enjoy world-class events like Formula 1 and MotoGP surrounded by scenic mountains and rolling hills. It was the perfect choice for our long exposure car photo idea 😁💚 AD #visitmurtal #visitsteiermark #creativephotography #longexposure #lightpainting

Broken Lens 📸 Biking on the Schneealm 📍 @visithochsteiermark AD We captured this image on the Schneealm, located in Hochsteiermark, Styria. To create a unique visual effect, we took an old camera lens protection glass and deliberately broke it using a nail and a hammer. Positioning this fractured glass in front of our camera's actual lens then produced the illusion that the lens itself was shattered. The Hochsteiermark famed mountain biking trails and picturesque mountain landscapes offered the ideal setting to execute this creative concept. 🚴⛰️ #hochsteiermark #visitsteiermark #creativephotography #photoideas

Camera flaring ✨ at Ausseerland Salzkammergut, Styria 📍 @Ausseerland AD Out in the Ausseerland, we played with sunlight and mirrors to create floating orbs of light by reflecting the sunlight into the camera lens. It felt like bending nature just a little, in the most beautiful way. Shot this magic at Lake Altaussee, right beneath the majestic Trisselwand. ✨☀️🪞🌊 #ausseerland #visitsteiermark #creativephotography #artist #photography

Mountain Cave Video Trick ⛰️ at @gesäuse , Styria 📍 We build a tiny cave out of stones for this optical illusion video trick. The Gesäuse region in Styria, Austria, was the perfect location for it, as it's dramatic alpine landscape known for its towering limestone peaks, deep gorges, and the wild Enns River, making it a paradise for nature lovers and photographers like us. 😁📸 AD #gesäuse #gesaeuse #photography #photoart

Two Worlds ✨ at Murau, Styria 📍@Steiermark - Das Grüne Herz AD We went all the way to Murau to try out a new panorama photo trick — couldn’t have picked a better spot. This place just has that calm, honest beauty that makes everything feel a bit more special. 🌄📱💫 #visitmurau #visitsteiermark #creativephotography #photoideas

Fake Ice Crack 🧊❄️ captured with Insta360 Go Ultra @insta360dach AD This tiny camera is perfect for all those moments when other cameras are simply too big 🫠 #insta360 #insta360goultra #videographytips #creativeideas

A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: Here today, gone tomorrow. You sacrifice your whole life for a title or a position, but you’ll be replaced sooner or later. Even your family will learn to live without you. That’s the reality. So don’t spend your life chasing people’s approval. Live for the One who never forgets. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: It’s interesting how we as humans work. When someone talks all the time, their words can slowly lose weight. But when a person stays quiet, and only speaks once in a while, people listen differently. Because you know what they’re saying has been reflected upon. Silence can indeed put weight in your words when you do choose to speak. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: Whatever hardship you are going through, know that it’s a blessing. It might not feel like it now, but it’s shaping you, humbling you, and bringing you closer to Allah.#lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: We think that if you put your full trust in Allah, your problems will suddenly disappear. But that’s never been the case. Life will still test you, and you’ll still feel pain. What changes is your heart. You carry the same struggles, but what Allah gives you is a calm, is a relief, so that no struggle you'll face will ever be able to break you. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: We call something “good” when it feels easy. And we call it “bad” the moment it hurts. But that’s only our limited view. Both ease and hardship carry lessons. One shapes your gratitude, the other shapes your patience. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: Everyone wants to change the world. But the truth is, the world is just a reflection of the people in it. Fix yourself, and you’ve already started fixing your surroundings. A better you means a better family, a better community, and a better world. Real change always starts in the mirror. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: One day, we’ll stand before Allah. And how we treat the standing now will shape how we stand then. Don’t let salah become something you rush or overlook. It’s your chance to prepare for the day when nothing else will matter. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

bio:
A small reminder, 
I just reflect as your brother. 
Copenhagen.
@Halal Hygge
video_name: What makes it hurt the most is when someone you helped turns against you. It feels heavier than being wronged by a stranger. But the good you did was never about them in the first place. Allah gave you the chance, and the guidance to do good.  So if they let you down, don’t carry it in your heart. Your reward isn’t with people. It’s with Allah. #lifelessons #lifereminder #foryou

video_name: Imagens recém-enviadas aos Arquivos Nacionais dos Estados Unidos reacenderam o debate sobre o lendário incidente de Roswell, de 1947. As fotos mostram destroços espalhados por uma grande cratera no deserto do Novo México, cena que muitos associam aos relatos de uma suposta queda de objeto voador não identificado. A autenticidade do material ainda não foi confirmada, mas o vazamento já alimenta novas teorias sobre um dos episódios mais emblemáticos da ufologia mundial. fonte : DailyMail  #roswell #vazou #alien #uap #ovni

video_name: Durante entrevista ao jornalista Ross Coulthart, o ex-Boina Verde Mike Battista , conhecido no meio ufológico como “Magic” Mike , afirmou que o chamado Fenômeno anômalo pode “aparecer para dizer olá” e que responde quando ele apenas pensa a respeito.  Segundo Battista, a interação sugere que o fenômeno teria natureza “quântica” e não poderia ser documentado com facilidade por tecnologias convencionais, desafiando a busca por imagens de alta definição. A entrevista de Ross Coulthart com Mike “Magic” Battista, está disponível no YouTube, no canal oficial New Nation do programa Reality Check. #pesquisadoresovni #uap #mistery #ovni #ufo

video_name: Um relatório do Centro de Estudos de Isótopos Aplicados da Universidade da Geórgia, divulgado pelo Dr. Steven Greer, analisou a resina encontrada na chamada Esfera Buga.  Segundo o documento, a amostra de resina foi cuidadosamente tratada em banho de ultrassom, limpa de possíveis carbonatos e seca antes da análise por espectrometria de massa de aceleração, processo que permite medir a idade de materiais orgânicos com precisão. O resultado indica que a resina possui cerca de 12.560 anos, tornando o artefato incrivelmente antigo. Esse material orgânico pode fornecer pistas sobre a origem e a composição da esfera, que apresenta uma estrutura metálica única e microesferas internas. #pesquisadoresovni #misterio #esferabuga  #ovni #uap

video_name: Em 1º de setembro de 2024, o pesquisador @f_gerson_meneses , do Projeto Artes do Bitorocaia, divulgou um estudo mostrando semelhanças entre pinturas rupestres do Arco do Covão, em Caxingó (Piauí), e de Daulatpur, na Índia. As imagens apresentam formas que lembram árvores e frutos, com 13 vetores convergindo para o centro, criando um padrão semelhante nos dois continentes. Enquanto a pintura indiana mostra uma árvore frutífera com um antropomorfo escalando os galhos, o painel brasileiro tem interpretação mais aberta, possivelmente ligada a sentimentos ou ideias abstratas. A descoberta evidencia como povos distantes, separados por milênios, encontraram maneiras parecidas de expressar sua relação com a natureza e com o imaginário humano. #pesquisadoresovni #descoberta #desconhecido #Unknown #rupestre

video_name: 🚨💥😉 MISTÉRIO NO CÉU DE TORONTO: OBJETO EM FORMA DE ARRAIA INTRIGA TESTEMUNHAS Um objeto voador não identificado foi registrado em Toronto, Canadá, no dia 20/09/2025, por volta das 17h45. O vídeo, com quase dois minutos de duração, mostra um objeto com formato semelhante a uma arraia refletindo a luz do sol, somente na ponta do objeto , enquanto plana e alterna movimentos verticais e velocidade. video_name: Em 5 de maio de 2024, a fotógrafa profissional Anna Ida Guida capturou um intrigante objeto voador não identificado sobre os céus de Celle di Bulgheria, no sul da Itália.  Segundo Guida, o objeto apareceu de forma repentina enquanto ela fotografava o céu para mostrar ao namorado o clima do dia. Curiosamente, o OVNI não estava presente em um segundo clique feito segundos depois, nem foi visto ou ouvido a olho nu.  o formato do objeto é semelhante ao que postamos recentemente em nosso perfil sobre um avistamento em Toronto, no Canadá. #pesquisadoresovni #uap #italy #ovni #ufo

video_name: 🚨💥 MISTÉRIO NO CÉU DE BAGDÁ: TESTEMUNHA REGISTRA OVNI DE FORMATO PECULIAR Um seguidor da página entrou em contato conosco e compartilhou um registro impressionante feito em Bagdá, no Iraque, no dia 04/04/2025. Segundo o relato, o objeto se movia rapidamente pelo céu e apresentava um formato incomum, diferente de qualquer aeronave ou fenômeno conhecido. A testemunha afirmou que jamais havia visto algo semelhante. O registro chama a atenção não apenas pela clareza, mas também pela raridade de casos divulgados naquela região do Oriente Médio, o que reforça ainda mais o caráter enigmático do episódio. Esse avistamento se soma a uma série de ocorrências recentes em diversas partes do mundo, sugerindo que estamos diante de um fenômeno global cada vez mais difícil de ignorar. #pesquisadoresovni #baghadad  #uap #ovni #ufo

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Un homme affirme que ChatGPT lui a révélé qui est l’Antéchrist 😳 En posant des questions simples sur les esprits, les anges et les démons, il dit avoir reçu des réponses troublantes… Certains parlent même d’un danger spirituel 👁️ Et vous, qu’en pensez-vous vraiment ?  #mystère #paranormal #révélation #étrange

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Et toi, est-ce que tu aurais gardé ça chez toi ? 🤯 Un homme a ramassé une météorite tombée du ciel… mais en la ramenant chez lui, une créature étrange a commencé à en sortir. Chaque jour, elle grandissait de plus en plus, se transformant en quelque chose d’inquiétant… Certains disent que c’est de la science-fiction, d’autres jurent que c’est réel 👽🔥 Et toi, tu en penses quoi ? #paranormal #mystère #ovni #alien #phénomène

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Tout commençait comme une simple histoire d’amour en ligne 💻 mais quand elle est arrivée chez eux à minuit pile 🕛 tout a basculé 😱 son regard n’avait rien d’humain… et dans son sac se cachait quelque chose qu’ils n’auraient jamais dû trouver 👁️ depuis ce jour, leur vie n’a plus jamais été la même 💀 #histoirevraie #mystère #paranormal #frissons #cauchemar

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Qu’est-ce que t’aurais fait toi ? 👀 Une fille voit sa sœur alors qu’elle était censée être ailleurs… Cette histoire de Doppelganger rend fou tout internet. 🕵️‍♂️ #doppelganger #histoirevirale #frissons #mystère #paranormal

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Tout semblait normal dans ce salon… jusqu’à ce que la main du teddy bear bouge toute seule 😰 La femme a senti qu’il y avait quelque chose de pas net, mais son mari a refusé de la croire… jusqu’à ce que la peluche commence à réagir devant leurs yeux 👁️ Ce qui est arrivé ensuite dépasse l’imagination 🧸🔥 #mystère #paranormal #frisson #histoire #inexpliqué

bio: 👻 Histoires paranormales & mystères inexpliqués
video_name: Un camion de glace filmé en pleine nuit… dans une rue complètement vide… aucune lumière, aucun enfant… mais des bruits étranges à l’intérieur 😰 Depuis le début du mois, plusieurs disparitions inexpliquées ont été signalées en Virginie 🧊 Et à chaque fois, un camion similaire aurait été vu quelques heures avant 👁️ Simple coïncidence ou quelque chose de beaucoup plus sombre ? Tu te sentirais en sécurité si ce camion s’arrêtait devant chez toi à 3h du mat ? 😶‍🌫️ #paranormal #mystère #camiondeglace #disparition #enquête

video_name: Falamos sobre um verme assustador que pode viver dentro de você por anos, chegando a mais de dez metros de comprimento e só saindo quando você vê pedaços dele nas suas fezes. Esse parasita entra no corpo pelo que comemos, como carne mal passada ou comida contaminada, e suga todos os seus nutrientes, deixando você fraco. Muitas pessoas não sentem nada, mas os sinais mais comuns são dor abdominal, emagrecimento rápido e até pedaços do verme aparecendo no vaso sanitário. Alguns casos extremos envolvem vermes de quase dois metros saindo do corpo, como o de um homem que adorava comer sashimi de salmão cru todos os dias. O mais assustador é que esses vermes podem viver por até trinta anos dentro de uma pessoa, crescendo cada vez mais. #vermedafita #parasita #sashimicru #intestino #fezes

video_name: Alessandro Venier: aggiornamenti sul possibile movente e sul passato dell’uomo. Dalle prime indagini su di lui e sulla sua famiglia, è emerso che Alessandro era un ragazzo problematico fin da bambino. Il rapporto con sua madre e con la sua compagna è stato definito come “burrascoso”, senza entrare però in troppi dettagli. La cosa certa è che Lorena Venier, sua madre, ha dichiarato che il figlio era violento nei confronti della sua compagna; il che, le avrebbe spinte ad agire in questa maniera.  Tornando al passato di Alessandro, si sa che su di lui pendeva una condanna che stava per diventare esecutiva e che gli avrebbe impedito l’espatrio. La causa? Una serie di piccoli reati commessi in passato e in tempi diversi. Questo è il motivo per cui aveva in programma di trasferirsi in Colombia con la sua compagna e sua figlia il prima possibile. Tra i reati, lesioni personali gravi, coltivazione di sostanze illecite e attività non autorizzate di recupero di residuati bellici.  Alle superiori gli era stato contestato il reato di procurato allarme e quello di minacce. E più tardi sarebbe stato protagonista anche di un episodio violento nei confronti di un ex collega. Ma si parla anche maltrattamenti di animali e numerosi atti di esibizionismo. Per ultimo, ma non per importanza, è da sottolineare che i maltrattamenti su sua madre e sulla sua compagna erano sempre più frequenti, e i carabinieri erano anche intervenuti più volte. Ora restano da accertare le dinamiche familiari, il reale movente e le accuse contro le due donne. Quando ci saranno aggiornamenti vi racconterò tutto!

video_name: En 1996, un hombre salió a caminar con su perro en los bosques del estado de Washington... y volvió con algo imposible. Dijo haber enfrentado a un ser que no era humano, lo envolvió y lo ocultó durante años. Nadie le creyó. Lo llamaron mentiroso, loco... un farsante más. > Pero algo no encaja. Años después, se filtraron imágenes inquietantes. No son animaciones. No son efectos especiales. Son reales. O al menos… parecen demasiado reales. Y lo que muestran, podría cambiarlo todo. Mira bajo tu propio riesgo. #actividadparanormalx #actividadparanormal #aliens #ufo #extraterrestre

bio: Lo inexplicable, Lo Paranormal, Lo Misterioso, Lo que nadie te cuenta.👁️👽

En una sala blanca, sin ventanas, los cuerpos de seres no humanos son manipulados por equipos médicos soviéticos, mientras oficiales de alto rango observan sin emitir palabra. Algunos están vivos. Otros… no tanto. ¿Qué hacían allí? ¿Cómo llegaron? ¿Y por qué este material fue ocultado por más de 40 años?
